---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Discover the Pomodoro technique and how our app helps you maximize productivity with deep focus sessions."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-16">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="text-center space-y-6 py-8">
      <div class="text-6xl mb-4">üçÖ</div>
      <h1
        class="text-5xl font-extrabold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-secondary to-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        The Pomodoro Technique
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-base-content/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A simple yet powerful method to improve your focus and productivity
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- What is Pomodoro -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">
        What is the Pomodoro Technique?
      </h2>
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            The Pomodoro Technique was created by <span
              class="font-bold text-primary">Francesco Cirillo</span
            > in the late 1980s. The name comes from the tomato-shaped kitchen timer
            (pomodoro in Italian) he used during university.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            This technique breaks work into <span class="badge badge-primary"
              >25-minute</span
            > intervals called "pomodoros", separated by short breaks. It's perfect
            for fighting procrastination and maintaining focus.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How it Works -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">How Does it Work?</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div
          class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-primary/5 border border-primary/20"
        >
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="badge badge-primary badge-lg">1</div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Choose a task</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              Select the task you want to work on. It can be anything: studying,
              coding, writing, designing...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/10 to-secondary/5 border border-secondary/20"
        >
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="badge badge-secondary badge-lg">2</div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Work for 25 minutes</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              Focus completely on your task for 25 minutes. No distractions, no
              social media, no multitasking.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-accent/5 border border-accent/20"
        >
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="badge badge-accent badge-lg">3</div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Take a 5-minute break</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              Take a short break. Stand up, stretch, drink water. Let your mind
              relax.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-info/10 to-info/5 border border-info/20"
        >
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="badge badge-info badge-lg">4</div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Repeat and long break</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              After 4 pomodoros, take a longer break of 15-30 minutes. You've
              earned it!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- App Features -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">App Features</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center text-primary">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="40"
              height="40"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mb-3"
              ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline
                points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg
            >
            <h3 class="card-title text-base-content">Smart Timer</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">
              Automatically alternates between work and rest. Set your available
              time and start.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center text-secondary">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="40"
              height="40"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mb-3"
              ><path d="M6 8a6 6 0 0 1 12 0c0 7 3 9 3 9H3s3-2 3-9"></path><path
                d="M10.3 21a1.94 1.94 0 0 0 3.4 0"></path></svg
            >
            <h3 class="card-title text-base-content">Notifications</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">
              Get sound alerts when each session ends. Never lose your rhythm.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center text-accent">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="40"
              height="40"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mb-3"
              ><path d="M3 3v18h18"></path><path d="m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <h3 class="card-title text-base-content">Detailed Stats</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">
              Visualize your weekly and daily performance. See how much real
              time you spend on each task.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center text-info">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="40"
              height="40"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mb-3"
              ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line
                x1="2"
                y1="12"
                x2="22"
                y2="12"></line><path
                d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <h3 class="card-title text-base-content">Multilingual</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">
              Available in Spanish and English. Switch languages anytime.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center text-warning">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="40"
              height="40"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mb-3"
              ><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"
              ></rect><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"></line></svg
            >
            <h3 class="card-title text-base-content">Responsive</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">
              Works perfectly on mobile, tablet, and desktop. Take your
              productivity everywhere.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center text-primary">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="40"
              height="40"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mb-3"
              ><path
                d="M19 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z"
              ></path><polyline points="17 21 17 13 7 13 7 21"
              ></polyline><polyline points="7 3 7 8 15 8"></polyline></svg
            >
            <h3 class="card-title text-base-content">History & Sync</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">
              Save your progress automatically. Analyze your sessions and keep
              track over time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Benefits of Using Pomodoro</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-primary">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle
                cx="12"
                cy="12"
                r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Improves concentration</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">
              Short intervals help you maintain focus without mental exhaustion.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-secondary">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path d="m12 14 4-4"></path><path
                d="M3.34 19a10 10 0 1 1 17.32 0"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Reduces procrastination</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">
              25 minutes is a manageable commitment. It's easier to start when
              you know it's temporary.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-accent">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path
                d="M12 22a7 7 0 0 0 7-7c0-2-1-3.9-3-5.5s-3-4-4-6.5c-1 2.5-2 4.9-4 6.5s-3 3.5-3 5.5a7 7 0 0 0 7 7Z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Prevents burnout</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">
              Regular breaks prevent exhaustion and keep your energy high.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-info">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path d="M13 2 3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Increases productivity</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">
              Working in short sprints makes you more efficient and time-aware.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="text-center space-y-6 py-8">
      <div
        class="card bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/20 via-secondary/20 to-accent/20 border border-primary/30"
      >
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title text-3xl justify-center mb-4">
            Ready to be more productive?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6">
            Start your first Pomodoro now and experience the difference
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-center">
            <a href="/en" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
              Start Now
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="h-6 w-6"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
